IRenderItem --|> ITransformable : requires
IMovable ..> ITransformable : uses
MovementManager ..> ITransformable : uses
ICollidable ..> ITransformable : uses

note bottom of IRenderItem
  **rendering requires transform**
  - position for draw location
  - size for draw dimensions
end note

note bottom of IMovable
  **movement modifies transform**
  - updates position based on velocity
  - respects acceleration
end note

note bottom of MovementManager
  **manager uses transform**
  - reads position for bounds checking
  - clamps position to world bounds
end note

note bottom of ICollidable
  **collision uses transform**
  - getBounds() constructs Rectangle
  - uses position + size
end note

